org.springframework.kafka.listener

接口 GenericMessageListener<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - the type received by the listener.
    所有已知子接口:
    AcknowledgingConsumerAwareMessageListener<K,V>, AcknowledgingMessageListener<K,V>, BatchAcknowledgingConsumerAwareMessageListener<K,V>, BatchAcknowledgingMessageListener<K,V>, BatchConsumerAwareMessageListener<K,V>, BatchMessageListener<K,V>, ConsumerAwareMessageListener<K,V>, MessageListener<K,V>
    所有已知实现类:
    BatchMessagingMessageListenerAdapter, FilteringBatchMessageListenerAdapter, FilteringMessageListenerAdapter, RecordMessagingMessageListenerAdapter, RetryingMessageListenerAdapter
    函数接口:
    这是一个函数接口, 因此可用作 lambda 表达式或方法引用的赋值目标。

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface GenericMessageListener<T>
    Top level interface for listeners.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.1

    • 方法详细资料

      • onMessage

        void onMessage(T data)
        Invoked with data from kafka.
        参数:
        data - the data to be processed.

      • onMessage

        default void onMessage(T data,
                       Acknowledgment acknowledgment)
        Invoked with data from kafka. The default implementation throws UnsupportedOperationException.
        参数:
        data - the data to be processed.
        acknowledgment - the acknowledgment.

      • onMessage

        default void onMessage(T data,
                       org.apache.kafka.clients.consumer.Consumer<?,?> consumer)
        Invoked with data from kafka and provides access to the Consumer for operations such as pause/resume. Invoked with null data when a poll returns no data (enabling resume). The default implementation throws UnsupportedOperationException.
        参数:
        data - the data to be processed.
        consumer - the consumer.
        从以下版本开始:
        2.0

      • onMessage

        default void onMessage(T data,
                       Acknowledgment acknowledgment,
                       org.apache.kafka.clients.consumer.Consumer<?,?> consumer)
        Invoked with data from kafka and provides access to the Consumer for operations such as pause/resume. Invoked with null data when a poll returns no data (enabling resume). The default implementation throws UnsupportedOperationException.
        参数:
        data - the data to be processed.
        acknowledgment - the acknowledgment.
        consumer - the consumer.
        从以下版本开始:
        2.0
